Package: textplot
Title: Text Oriented Plotting
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Tyler", "Rinker", email = "tyler.rinker@gmail.com", role = c("aut",
          "cre")))
Maintainer: Tyler Rinker <tyler.rinker@gmail.com>
Description: Analyze text data via serveral common text plotting methods. Methods include
          lexical dispersion plots, tree maps, speech networks, speech Gantt charts, text
          hilighting, word clouds, etc.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2)
Imports: data.table, dplyr, ggplot2, grDevices, plotrix, rstudioapi, stats, stringi, quanteda, wordcloud,
          textshape, utils
Suggests: testthat
Date: 2017-05-27
License: GPL-2
LazyData: TRUE
Roxygen: list(wrap = FALSE)
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
